      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Wide open race with a few in form and a couple with big ratings coming off poor runs. SHISUTA BO (4) led throughout at first run for the new yard to score a comfortable win. Extra trip a plus now and will take catching again. AWASH (5) tried hard but was no match for SHISUTA BO last time. Has a top record course and distance and deserves to break through. VENTING (2) ran on hard to arrive in time to score last time. In top form and drawn for a soft run. WINE BARRON (6) was well off best first try here and worth another chance. Best form stacks up and extra trip is a plus. PRINCE JOFRA (3) is having first run for new yard and will be winding up late.",
